#!/usr/bin/env bash
# i2i-inpaint-outpaint-decay-risk-.sh — 图生图 + 局部重绘修图（I2I + inpaint/outpaint + 修脸换脸）(Decay risk: medium) last_updated: 2026-06-22 SOP walkthrough for AIGC 创作工作流.
